**Proposed Enhanced Version:**
```bash
# JCScripts Configuration File
# This file configures the behavior of the script collection

# Preferred text editor for editing scripts
EDITOR="vi"

# Directory where scripts are installed
SCRIPTS_DIR="~/.scripts"

# GitHub repository configuration
GITHUB_USER="jcgarcia"
GITHUB_REPO_NAME="jcscripts"
GITHUB_REPO="git@github.com:${GITHUB_USER}/${GITHUB_REPO_NAME}.git"

# SSH key for GitHub authentication
# Generate with: ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -f ~/.ssh/jcscripts_deploy_key
SSH_KEY="~/.ssh/jcscripts_deploy_key"

# Backup directory for WSL distributions (Windows path via WSL)
BACKUP_DIR="/mnt/c/backup/wsl"

# Enable debug output (true/false)
DEBUG="false"

# Script collection version
SCRIPTS_VERSION="1.0"
```

