- ✅ Old versions properly archived
- ✅ Unrelated files removed (etc/caddy)
- ✅ .gitignore properly configured
- ✅ Repository architecture properly understood
- 🔄 Documentation alignment needed (minor)
- 🔄 Log file cleanup (minor)

